=== Etymology ===
[[Pig Latin]] version of [[fuck you]].

===Interjection===
'''uckfay ouyay''' 
# slightly less offensive variation of [[fuck you]]

Uckfay ouyay: sualluay cceptedaay saay omethyingsay eryvey ierdway. Anymay eoplepay ohway reay uenflay niay igpay atinlay ancay indfay isthsy atherray offensivoay. For the rest of us, it is normally fine. 

